Package: dmltree
Type: Package
Title: DML Causal Estimation with Interpretable Trees
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Denis", "Agniel", email = "dagniel@rand.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements methods for causal inference using Double Machine Learning (DML)
    with interpretable tree-based models. This package builds on optimaltrees to provide
    DML-based causal estimation with tree-based machine learning methods.
